India approves 350 - mln - rupee GE subsidiary . The Indian Industry Ministry said on Wednesday that it approved a 350 - million - rupee investment by a unit of U . S . - based General Electric Co ( GE ) in a lighting components subsidiary . The investment was among 58 proposals worth a total of 6 . 6 billion rupees which were approved by the Foreign Investment Promotion Board , it said in a statement . It said GE Lighting ( India ) Ltd would set up the wholly - owned subsidiary in Bombay . - - New Delhi newsroom + 91 - 11 301 2024 
